item.title: CVE-2020-1897|2024-08-04T06:53:59.853Z -- facebook -- proxygen
item.description: A use-after-free is possible due to an error in lifetime management in the request adaptor when a malicious client invokes request error handling in a specific sequence. This issue affects versions of proxygen prior to v2020.05.18.00.
